https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-configure-the-nginx-web-server-on-a-virtual-private-server

Nginx Configuration Directory Hierarchy
Nginx stores its configuration files within the "/etc/nginx" directory.

Inside of this directory, you will find a few directories and various modular configuration files:

cd /etc/nginx
ls -F
conf.d/         koi-win           naxsi.rules   scgi_params       uwsgi_params
fastcgi_params  mime.types        nginx.conf    sites-available/  win-utf
koi-utf         naxsi_core.rules  proxy_params  sites-enabled/

If you are coming from Apache, 
the "sites-available" and "sites-enabled" directories will be familiar.

These directories are used to define configurations for your websites. 
Files are generally created in the "sites-available" directory, 
and then symbolically linked to the "sites-enabled" directory when they are ready to go live.


-----------------------------------------------
HEAD detached at release-1.11.3 从源码编译安装，后
-----------------------------------------------
/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf

    server {
        listen       80;
        server_name  localhost;

        #charset koi8-r;

        #access_log  logs/host.access.log  main;

        location / {
            root   html; 指定的是 /usr/local/nginx 目录下的 html 目录
            index  index.html index.htm;
        }

这里 指定目录是：
/usr/local/nginx/html 
问题，在哪里指定的？

修改root目录到
root   /Users/wangxiang/sharedir/www;
重新加载配置文件
sudo /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -s reload
再访问服务器，出错：
403 Forbidden
查看，指定的目录的权限信息：
drwxr-xr-x  3 wangxiang  staff  102  9 29 00:17 www
其上级目录的权限是：
drwx------   5 wangxiang  staff         170  9 29 00:12 sharedir
修改成 704 不行
drwx---r--   5 wangxiang  staff         170  9 29 00:12 sharedir
修改成 705 就可以了
drwx---r-x   5 wangxiang  staff         170  9 29 00:12 sharedir

nginx 进程，所属的用户
mac-mini:~ wangxiang$ ps aux | grep nginx
nobody            739   0.0  0.0  2453496   1252   ??  S    12:32上午   0:00.01 nginx: worker process
root              738   0.0  0.0  2444052    388   ??  Ss   12:32上午   0:00.00 nginx: master process /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx

